window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Benny</b></p> <p>Big Bend is my home. I love it here. I love everything about it.</p> <p>It's my senior year, and I'm determined to have the best one yet. Of course, that's when life gets confusing.</p> <p>I think I may have a little bit of a crush on my nemesis.</p> <p>Something I never saw coming.</p> <p>I just hope I can find a way to make him give me a chance because being together would make not only this year great but this life of ours—absolutely epic.</p> <p><b>Rowan</b></p> <p>Benjamin McBride is the bane of my existence. He simply won't quit—he never does.</p> <p>He's too happy. Too confident. Too unafraid.</p> <p>I can't let him get to me.</p> <p>He thinks we could be epic together, that us in a relationship would be some saving grace—a Hail Mary—a way to make this year and our lives the best they can be.</p> <p>But I'm not destined for happiness.</p> <p>I have to make him understand.</p> <p>It's never going to happen.</p>"; 
